# Monorepo ignore rules (ASP.NET + Node/Next + common tooling)

# --- OS / Editor ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp
*.bak
*.log

# --- Environment / secrets ---
.env*

# --- IDEs ---
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# --- .NET / Visual Studio build outputs ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
artifacts/
TestResults/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
NuGet.Config.user

# --- Node / Next.js ---
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.turbo/
**/.vercel/
**/.cache/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Project-specific ---
/backend/dist/
/backend/logs/
/backend/tmp/
